## Create a Spring boot application as student-management-app

## Create 1st microservice as called student-app

It has four controller  (Caller)

/student/save  @RequestBody Student

/student/read  Read all student

/student/update (requestparam name, update age) update student age using name

/student/delete  (requestparam name) delete student using name

## Create Second Microservice  calles school-operation  (Receiver)

/school/save   @RequestBody Student
/school/read   Read all student
/school/update (requestparam name, update age) update student age using name
/school/delete  (requestparam name) delete student using name

## Detail of Modle Student

String id
String name
String schoolName
int age
String gender

Json Model

    {
         "name":"student1",
         "schoolName": "school1",
         "age":17,
         "gender": "M",
    }

 Develop This project using TDD and test coverage should be more than 80%

 All the data should get store in Mysql Database

 Create Readme file which contain the all steps


